  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>"Browse Playbooks" affordance mounted at the audit-recommended location in briefing widget</criterion>
    <criterion>Click opens Dialog wrapping PlaybookLibraryShell — mirrors task 094 wiring pattern</criterion>
