    <criterion>Clicking a playbook invokes it through Path A.5 routing (verified manually)</criterion>
    <criterion>NO direct call to AnalysisOrchestrationService.ExecuteAnalysisAsync</criterion>
    <criterion>ADR-021 dark mode compliance — semantic tokens only</criterion>
    <criterion>Component test passes</criterion>
    <criterion>npm run build:prod passes</criterion>
    <criterion>code-review + adr-check pass at Step 9.5 (FULL rigor)</criterion>
